### get partner call
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/partner/Partners
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### post partner call
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/partner/Partners
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Shweta",
  "email": "abc@deloitte.com",
  "phone": "9876543212"
}

### patch partner call
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/partner/Partners('387de2ee-e2af-4bd0-b833-18899c41d4f4')
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
"name": "Shweta1"
}

### Delete partner call
DELETE http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/partner/Partners('387de2ee-e2af-4bd0-b833-18899c41d4f4')
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

